</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-24_ pf-text-1">Survival rates plummet by 7-10% for every minute without defibrillation during SCA.&nbsp;</li><li data-pf-type="List2.Item2" class="sc-fXEqDS gMGtOR pf-26_ pf-text-1">AEDs increase the chance of survival by up to 75% when administered promptly.






























































